  ('f08d64cc-84e1-48c4-9fd7-7ecc88425ed0', 'KIMCHI-50', 'Wakame, dried seaweed 100g Nobi', 'Dried seaweed from the brown algae group, valued in Japanese cuisine for its mild taste and delicate texture. Commonly added to miso, ramen, and fish dishes.', 'Wakame, dried seaweed 100g Nobi', 'Dried seaweed from the brown algae group, valued in Japanese cuisine for its mild taste and delicate texture. Commonly added to miso, ramen, and fish dishes.'),
